data.title: Great Parks of Hamilton County
data.meta_description: Book the perfect picnic spot by contacting Great Parks of Hamilton County. Our best picnic grounds feature shelters, grills, and tables!
data.text:
Great Parks of Hamilton County offers 58 open-sided picnic shelters and 2 non-sheltered picnic areas that are available to reserve up to a year in advance. Use our search tool above to check the availability of reservable picnic areas in your favorite park. If you need assistance or more information, please contact Great Parks Guest Relations at 513-521-7275.

Catering and special packages are available at Miami Whitewater Forest, Sharon Woods and Winton Woods. For a full list of locations and menus, click here.
